org.cove.jade.primitives
Class Wheel

    java.lang.Object
    org.cove.jade.primitives.Particle
    org.cove.jade.primitives.CircleParticle
    org.cove.jade.primitives.Wheel
public class Wheel
extends CircleParticle

Class implementing a wheel. Note that wheel rotation is in world co-ordinates, not relative to whatever the wheel is attached to (in fact, the only way of attaching the wheel to anything is via constraints which do not give it a particular direction anyway as the wheel is referred to by its center). This means you can roll wheels that aren't attached to anything!

setTraction

    public void setTraction(double t)
Sets wheel traction (well, actually slip) - 0 = no slip/full traction, 1 = full slip/no traction. Note that the wheel may still "slip" with this set to 0 due to constraints, gravity, etc.
